org.apache.ignite.ml.dataset.impl.bootstrapping

Class BootstrappedVector

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.ignite.ml.structures.DatasetRow<Vector>
      • org.apache.ignite.ml.structures.LabeledVector<Double>
        • org.apache.ignite.ml.dataset.impl.bootstrapping.BootstrappedVector
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Externalizable, Serializable

    public class BootstrappedVector
extends LabeledVector<Double>
    Represents vector with repetitions counters for subsamples in bootstrapped dataset. Each counter shows the number of repetitions of the vector for the n-th sample.
